{"Sid":0,"Did":118157,"Id":"282305","Title":"羅東慶安宮石獅","ImageUrl":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-02-24/d8bcb89b-5364-472e-b2a1-718bfe1349c7/collection/cc3b8c27-3b17-4615-b8d4-2560fb3b3e55/108-her-pa-1839-201910261917065db42861cfcbb0.jpg / https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-02-24/d8bcb89b-5364-472e-b2a1-718bfe1349c7/collection/34f43c1c-b62e-4b56-9f87-d47fef4a4a73/108-her-pa-1839-201910261917065db42861cfcbb1.jpg","IndexCode":"Culture_Place","CustomColumns":{"Description":"\n\n在台灣傳統廟宇建築正面中門前，經常可見一對石獅，其功能與門枕石或石鼓相當，主要是做為廟宇高大門扇的穩定支撐構件，在象徵意義上也具有招福避邪的作用。 　　羅東慶安宮中門前配置一對石獅，兩獅的頭部均略轉向中門處。龍邊側石獅為公獅，右腳做戲球狀，胸前則有銅錢狀裝飾，其上刻有「昭和」「丙子」字樣，即慶安宮重建時間－1936（昭和11）年。羅東慶安宮因主神為鄭成功，因此頗多鄭氏人氏捐獻寄附，此座公石獅基座上即刻有「基隆鄭振芳敬」字樣，鄭振芳為基隆人，開設基隆運送株式會社等多家公司。 　　虎邊側為母獅小獅，在獅座刻有「平和材木店」、「許平敬献」字樣。許平乃羅東木材巨商許萬枝之父，雲林人，原在嘉義從事木材事業，太平山林場開發後，於1933年遷居羅東，開設平和材木店。\n\n","Keyword_Rights_2":"CC BY / CC BY","Keyword_Des_Rights_2":"CC0","Keyword_Longitude":"121.7702009","Keyword_Latitude":"24.6720481","Original_Url":"https://cmsdb.culture.tw/place/9471DDFE-B452-4DF9-9133-22A1424D76A4","Original_Identifier":"282305","Keyword_Subject_1":"民俗與宗教","alias":"","Keywords":"石獅 / 許平 / 開台聖王 / 慶安宮 / 鄭振芳 / 羅東","historicalDates":"","LastUpdateTime":"2020/02/24 15:17:23","timelines":"","place":"羅東鎮中正南路175號慶安宮","address":"宜蘭縣羅東鎮中正南路175號","longitude":"121.7702009","latitude":"24.6720481","phone":"","Event":"","relationPeople":"","open":"0","free":"否","openTime":"","openTimeDescription":"","capacity":"","traffic":"","subjection":"","tag":"","situation":"","historicalDataBrief":"","historicalData":"","reference":"","writer":"林鴻文/ 蔡明志","createOrgName":"宜蘭縣政府文化局","source":"","Keyword_Rights_1":"","AllImages":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-02-24/d8bcb89b-5364-472e-b2a1-718bfe1349c7/collectionOpen/04a29bbf-9019-48b9-9436-fe1acd28fd47/108-her-pa-1839-re-201910261919455db42861cfcbb0.jpg / https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-02-24/d8bcb89b-5364-472e-b2a1-718bfe1349c7/collectionOpen/8c5c2eb2-97af-4f9f-9ff2-f